OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy and
OL,6,Fdamp overnight with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspreading across the region,
OL,8,Fpotentially turning heavier in the far
OL,9,Fwest towards dawn. Low cloud becoming
OL,10,Fmore widespread, resulting in coastal
OL,11,Fand hill fog. Warm and muggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FWettest during the morning,
OL,14,Fthen rain turning patchier from the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Limited brightness emerging
OL,16,Fand remaining murky around coasts with
OL,17,Ffog lingering for some throughout
OL,18,FWednesday. Feeling humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
