OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRemaining humid on Thursday and Friday
OL,7,Fwith fog persisting around coasts
OL,8,Fwhilst brighter spells emerge inland.
OL,9,FLow cloud potentially clearing on
OL,10,FSaturday and feeling fresher.
